name: Githubeko erdi lurra
body:
### Welcome to Erdi Lurra
Erdi Lurra is the name of "Middle Earth" translated to basque.

The goal of this blog will be to share the thoughts, and doubts (mostly second) related to the development applications I'm involved in: my work, and my side project. Focused in JavaScript.

### Support or Contact
You can contact me at txusinho@gmail.com or by a pull request ;-P
